Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Assignment
    Represents assignments as a list of variables and their assigned value.
    Atom
    Represents an atom as a predicate and a list of its arguments.
    Constraint
    Represents a generic Constraint (abstract).
    ConstraintDif
    Represents equality constraints as a pair of variables that must be different.
    ConstraintEq
    Represents equality constraints as a pair of variables that must be equal.
    ConstraintExt
    Represents constraints in extension, as a list of variables and a list of valid tuples.
    CSP
    Represents an instance of CSP, aggregating a network of constraints and keeping track of the assignment(s).
    CstNetwork
    Represents a network of constraints (X,D,C).
    FactBase
    Represents a Facts Base FB, as a list of valid predicates (facts).
    Homomorphisms
    Represents all homomorphisms of a query Q in our facts base FB, and lets us convert them to a network of constraints.
    KnowledgeBase
    Represents a knowledge base containing a facts base and a set of rules.
    KnowledgeBaseInterrogator
    A simple class to test our knowledge base and run queries on it.
    Rule
    Represents a rule of the knowledge base.
    Term
    Represents and lets us manipulate logic terms as variables or 'constants'.
